---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ScreenshotPlaceholder from '../../components/ScreenshotPlaceholder.astro';
import CTASection from '../../components/CTASection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Narrative Strategy Backtest — TradeStudio" description="Monthly AI predictions from OHLCV data for any symbol. Cached predictions with incremental updates.">

  <section class="py-20 px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
      <div class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-accent-purple">AI Analysis</div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold md:text-5xl">Narrative Strategy Backtest</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg text-text-secondary">Monthly AI-generated predictions using only OHLCV price data. Works with any symbol. See how AI interprets pure price action — without fundamental data.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="px-6 pb-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
      <ScreenshotPlaceholder label="Narrative backtest summary with monthly predictions and accuracy" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-border bg-bg-secondary py-16 px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8">How it works</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-text-secondary">
        <p>The Narrative Strategy Backtest takes a different approach from the Earnings Backtest. Instead of analyzing transcripts, the AI looks at pure OHLCV (Open, High, Low, Close, Volume) data and generates monthly predictions.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 pl-4">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-accent-purple">&#8226;</span> Works with any symbol — not just stocks with earnings transcripts</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-accent-purple">&#8226;</span> The AI analyzes monthly price patterns, trends, and volume</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-accent-purple">&#8226;</span> Predictions include direction, magnitude, and confidence</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-accent-purple">&#8226;</span> Results are cached locally — pay once, reuse forever</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-accent-purple">&#8226;</span> New months are added incrementally as data becomes available</li>
        </ul>
        <p>This is a research tool for exploring whether AI can extract predictive signal from price action alone.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTASection
    title="Explore AI price predictions"
    subtitle="Test whether AI can read price action. For any symbol."
    primaryCta={{ label: 'Download Free', href: '/download' }}
  />

</BaseLayout>
